{"_path":"/zh/guide/introduction","_dir":"guide","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"介绍","description":null,"icon":"lucide:info","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"vue3-mobile-table 是一个轻量级解决方案，专门用于弥合桌面表格组件与移动端触摸交互之间的体验差距。通过一个简单的指令，它可以让任何 Vue PC 表格组件（ 例如：Element Plus、Ant Design Vue、Naive UI 等UI库中的 Table 组件）在移动设备上也能获得接近原生级、丝滑流畅的滚动与交互体验。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"核心特性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心特性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"物理仿真引擎"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 基于 Delta Time 的帧率归一化，消除任意刷新率屏幕之间的速度差异，提供一致的惯性体感。内置惯性保护：手指停顿超过 80ms 再松开时自动清零速度，防止误触发惯性滚动"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"方向轴锁定"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 在每次触摸开始时自动判定手势意图，过滤对角线抖动，整个手势期间只锁定在一个轴向（横向或纵向）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智能边缘感知"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 滚动触达边界时自动交还控制权给浏览器，兼容 iOS 侧滑返回等原生行为"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"急停点击保护"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 区分\"用户想点击\"与\"用户想刹车\"，仅在高速惯性滚动时拦截点击事件，防止误触"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多指追踪与锁定"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 通过 Touch ID 追踪锁定活跃手指，防止多指交替导致的坐标跳变。检测到多指时引擎完全静默，将控制权交还浏览器处理原生手势（如缩放）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"UI 库预设"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 内置 Element Plus、Ant Design Vue、Naive UI、VxeTable、Arco Design、PrimeVue、Vuetify 等主流 UI 库的预设配置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合设备懒接管"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 四态状态机（dormant/standby/pending-active/active）：纯 PC 零侵入，混合设备（Surface / 触屏笔记本）按需劫持，通过 pending-active 中间态消除误触激活"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS 旋转坐标逆变换"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 支持 CSS "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transform: rotate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 横屏场景，通过离散角度轴交换自动矫正触摸坐标，零三角函数开销"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"零依赖"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 纯原生实现，无需额外依赖"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"解决了什么问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"解决了什么问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vue 生态中尚未出现可对标主流桌面表格栈的移动端 Table 方案。在报表等复杂业务场景下，移动端同样需要具备高性能与完整交互能力的表格组件，但当前生态存在明显空缺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实际落地通常只有两种路径：其一，自研表格组件，但触控交互、滚动机制与复杂功能实现成本极高，开发与维护负担沉重；其二，复用 Element Plus 等桌面端表格组件，但由于未针对移动端优化，在触控与小屏场景下普遍存在体验问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复用桌面表格时，常见痛点包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对角线滑动误触"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 用户本想横向查看表格数据，却因手指路径不直而意外触发页面纵向滚动，导致视线丢失"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"滚动方向不纯粹"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 手指轻微倾斜就可能在横纵轴之间频繁切换，滑动路径显得杂乱"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"滚动不跟手"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 在复杂 UI 组件嵌套场景中，原生 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"overflow: auto"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 常出现明显滞后"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺少惯性反馈"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 松手后滚动立即中断或惯性生硬，远距离浏览需要反复拖拽"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"表头滚动撕裂"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 表体滚动时固定表头无法像素级同步，出现错位或延迟"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不同设备体感差异"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 刷新率差异导致同一套代码在不同设备上手感不一致"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"手势冲突"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 多指操作坐标跳变，或边界处干扰 iOS 侧滑返回等系统手势"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"混合设备干扰"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — 在 Surface、触屏笔记本等设备上盲目劫持会影响鼠标与触控板使用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CSS 旋转横屏坐标错乱"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transform: rotate()"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 场景下触摸物理方向与逻辑滚动方向错位"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"v-mobile-table"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 通过接管触摸事件流，在指令内以滚动物理引擎应对上述问题；实现细节见 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/zh/how-it-works/how-it-works"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作原理"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"工作原理"},"children":[{"type":"tex